	--crf 19 slow
	Some people might wonder about some content that looks
	like commercials or promos but I've only left in the
	stuff that is in the middle of normal action or with
	overlapping audio or no blackframes in between. Runtime
	seems pretty constant at a few secs over 42 min on most
	episodes with that logic applied. At least all of it is
	poker and WPT related. 
	
	INFO:
	
	MINDTHEGAP is living up to its groupname. We do mind all
	the gaps in archives out there. If we see a rerun airing
	of unreleased eps from series we try to get it. If the
	show is really old and the hope of finding the original
	release is gone, we try to fix that too with iNTERNALs. 
	
	This of course makes our releases a bit random and some
	might think we are mad but there will be a reason behind
	the madness
